# WHAT IS THIS ?

# WOW NOW I WANT IT TOO

1. generate an ssh key
1. push the ssh key to github
1. clone the repo 
	```bash
		git clone https://github.com/robby0070/dotfiles .dotfiles
	```
2. create a python virtual environment (optional)
	```bash
		sudo apt install python3.11-venv # install the venv package
		python3 -m venv venv # create the venv
		. venv/scripts/activate # source the venv			
	```
3. run the install script
	```
		./install # for terminal-only apps
		./install_with_gui # for fully fledged DE settings and GUI apps
	```

